          "distinct": true,
          "id": "8bb9972a9a26f98c8ca82332f9b176e4c87cca70",
          "message": "fix(tm2): restore config TOML indentation to none (#5257)\n\nAt some point, a change (either in the in the node config marshaling\ncode or a version bump of the toml package in the `go.mod`) altered the\ndefault indentation of the config file generated by `gnoland config\ninit`. We can't revert this change since git history was rewritten.\n\nThis breaks the config diffs tracked in `misc/deployments`, where\nper-testnet config changes are reviewed as readable diffs. Indented\noutput makes those diffs noisy and hard to follow.\n\nThis fix switches from `toml.Marshal` to `toml.NewEncoder` with explicit\n`Indentation(\"\")` to enforce no indentation, restoring previous behavior\nwhile keeping the latest toml package v1.X version.",
          "timestamp": "2026-03-09T22:37:01+01:00",
          "tree_id": "fd3c35f371706966fb16c50453c923717dd51a72",
          "url": "https://github.com/gnolang/gno/commit/8bb9972a9a26f98c8ca82332f9b176e4c87cca70"
