          "distinct": true,
          "id": "afd7e48086f8742c4c5ff70bc7f594f3ec715963",
          "message": "feat(gnovm)!: move runtime to testing stdlibs (#5321)\n\nGC and MemStats are only used in filetests\n(gnovm/tests/files/alloc_*.gno) and have no legitimate use in on-chain\ncode. Keeping them in the production stdlibs would lock in\nimplementation details ŌĆö specifically, the allocator's internal\nbyte-counting format ŌĆö as part of the deterministic on-chain execution\nenvironment. Moving them to gnovm/tests/stdlibs/runtime/ ensures they\nare only available during testing and cannot be imported by realm or\npackage code deployed on-chain.\n\nBREAKING CHANGE: Backward incompatible with gnoland1.",
          "timestamp": "2026-03-23T11:58:12+01:00",
          "tree_id": "0a898192d85a5cf08460085fe4e38ece98c8aed2",
          "url": "https://github.com/gnolang/gno/commit/afd7e48086f8742c4c5ff70bc7f594f3ec715963"
