          "message": "chore(tm2): remove resolved TODO comments in `state/store.go` (#5290)\n\nRemove 4 'TODO: ensure that buf is completely read' comments as they are\nalready handled by `amino.Unmarshal`'s reflection path which checks n !=\nlen(bz) after decoding.\n\nAlso `PBMessager` is never implemented, so it always take the reflection\nbranch in `tm2/pkg/amino/amino.go:618`",
